<paragraph blockId="28.[151,1436,289,746]" pageId="28" pageNumber="29">
<materialsCitation ID-GBIF-Occurrence="3325287306" box="[151,948,289,314]" country="New Zealand" location="New Zealand" pageId="28" pageNumber="29" specimenCount="1">
The 
<typeStatus box="[205,253,290,314]" pageId="28" pageNumber="29">type</typeStatus>
species of this genus of nine species is from 
<collectingCountry box="[792,948,289,314]" name="New Zealand" pageId="28" pageNumber="29">New Zealand</collectingCountry>
</materialsCitation>
, and undescribed species are known from eastern 
<collectingCountry box="[241,347,325,350]" name="Australia" pageId="28" pageNumber="29">Australia</collectingCountry>
, but the other eight named species are recorded from the following parts of Asia: three from southern 
<collectingCountry box="[255,319,362,385]" name="Japan" pageId="28" pageNumber="29">Japan</collectingCountry>
of which one is also known from 
<collectingCountry box="[711,797,361,386]" name="Taiwan" pageId="28" pageNumber="29">Taiwan</collectingCountry>
; a second species was described from 
<collectingCountry box="[1234,1319,361,386]" name="Taiwan" pageId="28" pageNumber="29">Taiwan</collectingCountry>
, two from Peninsular 
<collectingCountry box="[276,382,397,422]" name="Malaysia" pageId="28" pageNumber="29">Malaysia</collectingCountry>
, one from 
<collectingCountry box="[501,601,397,422]" name="Thailand" pageId="28" pageNumber="29">Thailand</collectingCountry>
and one from the 
<collectingCountry box="[806,936,397,422]" name="Philippines" pageId="28" pageNumber="29">Philippines</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
